<br>
You look up to see an elven swordsman with sword in hand inspecting the fine craftmanship of the blade before him.  He jumps up to sit upon the trunk of a fallen tree.  With his legs hanging over the side, he casually drops his hands in his lap and rests his drawn sword across his chest against the opposite shoulder.<br>
<br>
He looks up and peers into your eyes and addresses you.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Let me introduce myself.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Sometimes I am laid back and slow placed while I hunt around.  Other times my tracking may detect an evil presence upon the lands OR I go out and seek specific monstrosities, and if I locate one, I try to muster the force to vanquish it.<br>
<br>
I conduct myself with honor and pride, and consider myself a traveller and even crypt robber of sorts.  I am loyal to my friends, and silent to my enemies.<br>
<br>
In a way I like to think of what I do as paralleling the mythical &quot;Indiana Jones, combined with He-man (because my mount reminds me of battlecat <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ), and Elbryan Wyndon (from the Demon Wars series <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ).&quot;<br>
<br>
I am no Robin Hood; ie, I do not donate to &quot;less fortunate&quot; strangers.  I am not greedy though, and I enjoy rewarding people for their time and effort when possible.  I believe in equality and believe in Need before Greed.<br>
<br>
<br>
So, why am I here talking to you?  <br>
<br>
<br>
I do <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">NOT</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> wish to form a guild.  I am looking to meet people for regular hunting; people around my season (60), (minimum 45+, preferably 50+) to on occasion seek out adventure, and seek out creatures to slaughter and pillage.<br>
<br>
When adventuring this way, I prefer to travel the countryside on the back our our mounts (horses or lizards).  I prefer to fight within enemy strongholds or dungeons.<br>
<br>
If you wish to join me <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>or</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> if you are a friend and can use my assistance, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>I can be found in the channel <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">LastCrusade</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> any day of the week that I am &quot;awake&quot;. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>((Note:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> I will always be in this channel, but I may not always be &quot;free&quot;.  I play on EST timezone and am not at home 7am - 6pm EST Mon-Fri.  <br>
<br>
Also, obligations to whatever guild I am in will have greater priority.  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>At the time of this posting, I am currently unguilded, though not for long.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->))<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>/End Note</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<br>
 <br>
Any of the following places (in no particular order) interest me. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LIST START--><ul><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Howling Stones / Charasis</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Old Sebilis</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Kael Drakkal</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Tower of Frozen Shadow</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Sirens Grotto</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li>Any Epic Piece Hunts that 1-2 groups can do</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Solusek B</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Giants or Lord Djinn or ...)</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Karnors Castle</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->(basement)</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>3rd Floor of Crypt of Dalnir</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (this place is level 30 - low 40's, but I don't care.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Hole</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (near Paineel)</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Maidens Eye</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Akheva Ruins</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Dragon Necropolis</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Deep</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Plane of Hate</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Plane of Fear</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Halls of Testing</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Temple of Veeshan)</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Western Wastes</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> animals and benevolence quest (must have at least dubious faction with Claws of Veeshan (Velious Dragons), which hunting in Kael will achieve.</li></ul><!--EZCODE LIST END--> <p><!-